graph LR
    LMEval["LMEval Job<br/>Batch Evaluation"]

    %% Internal RHOAI Dependencies
    LMEval -->|creates job| TrustyAI["TrustyAI LMEval<br/>Operator"]
    LMEval -->|status callbacks<br/>HTTPS/443| EvalHub["EvalHub Service"]
    LMEval -->|POST /v1/completions<br/>HTTP/HTTPS| Inference["Inference Endpoint<br/>vLLM / TGI"]
    LMEval -->|evaluation metrics<br/>HTTP/HTTPS| MLflow["MLflow Tracking<br/>Server"]

    %% External Service Dependencies
    LMEval -->|OCI artifact push<br/>HTTPS/443| Quay["OCI Registry<br/>Quay"]
    LMEval -->|datasets & tokenizers<br/>HTTPS/443| HFHub["HuggingFace Hub"]
    LMEval -->|offline test data<br/>HTTPS/443| S3["S3-compatible<br/>Storage"]

    %% Core Runtime Dependencies
    LMEval -->|runtime| Python["Python 3.11"]
    LMEval -->|tensor computation| PyTorch["PyTorch 2.6.0"]
    LMEval -->|tokenization| Transformers["transformers 4.48.0"]
    LMEval -->|data loading| Datasets["datasets 3.1.0"]
    LMEval -->|platform SDK| EvalHubSDK["eval-hub-sdk 0.1.5"]
    LMEval -->|text processing| Unitxt["unitxt 1.17.2"]
    LMEval -->|OCI artifacts| Skopeo["skopeo - system"]

    %% Orchestration
    TrustyAI -.->|watches LMEvalJob CR<br/>creates K8s Job| LMEval

    style LMEval fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

